%pyspark
df=getDataFrameFromHive()
df.show(10)
tdf = transformDataFrameToAssoicationAnalysis(df)
tdf.show(5,truncate=False)
print("There are "+str(tdf.count())+" orders");
model=train2Model(tdf,10,0.5,tdf.count())
#Display frequent itemsets.
model.freqItemsets.sort('freq',ascending=False).show()

%pyspark
df_=genPredictDataFrame(1000)
#consequents as prediction
df_predict=useModel(model,df_)
df_predict.show()
freqProductName=getItemListFromHive()
# show product name in rules
df=stockCode2stockName(df_predict,freqProductName)
df.show()
